  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the efficacy of pemoline in treating cocaine and/or
      methamphetamine dependent adults with comorbid Adult Attention Deficit Hyperactivity
      Disorder (ADHD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
